message.body: Guess whose groceries I just carried to their car? :)
He came in to the city for something and I ran into him at the food coop, wearing your sweatshirt.
Haha i love that. I love you both.
I'm doing well! I start seeing patients in clinic in three weeks or so! Elliott might come see me. He said Josey didn't quite finish the three part protocol Laura gave him.
How are you? Are you still in Florida? :)
Rad! Lets phone date in a couple days? Try me early week??
Outof florida!Headed to nola right now.almost there!
Ooooh awesome! Yes to a phone date! You call me or I'll call you. My schedule is erratic. I'm trying to be in bed by 9 or so. Be safe!!!! :) :) :) :)
